  "message": "feat(tests): Add beads test fixture directory\n\nAdd a test fixture directory for beads integration tests:\n\ntests/.beads/\n- .gitignore: Exclude database files, locks, and temp files\n- config.yaml: Standard beads project configuration\n- metadata.json: Database and export path metadata\n\nThis fixture enables integration tests to operate with a known beads\nconfiguration without affecting the main project's .beads/ directory.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>",
